

run the tests with:

$ python -m tests

Run the program with:

$ python -m pythontrainer

run coverage with (may need to conda install coverage or pip install coverage):

$ python -m coverage run -m tests

create the html report with:

$ python -m coverage html

then view the html report with (insert your own browser maybe):

$ browser htmlcov/index.html


View other style issues with pylint:

python -m pylint pythontrainer.py tests.py
